[\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Neon Alley Hip Tilt Smirk\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A young solo female model with long blonde hair and Korean facial features stands in a rain-slicked urban alley at night, bathed in vivid neon pink and blue light from surrounding signs. She leans confidently against a brick wall in a 3/4 angle from slightly below eye level, one hand resting on her hip, the other hand lightly touching her hair near her temple. She wears a sleek black high-fashion ensemble. Her expression is a cool, confident smirk — commanding and effortlessly stylish. The neon reflections pool on the wet ground beneath her. Shot on a 50mm lens, vogue-style editorial lighting, deep shadows with saturated color pops.\",\n    \"image_url\": \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nebulagg001-lgtm/ai-gallery/main/images/neon-alley-hip-tilt-smirk-20260304.png\",\n    \"date\": \"2026-03-04T02:16:00\",\n    \"category\": \"Pose\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Waitomo Glowworm Caves at Midnight — New Zealand\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A breathtaking underground cave system in Waitomo, New Zealand, photographed at midnight. The cave ceiling is blanketed with thousands of tiny bioluminescent glowworms (Arachnocampa luminosa), casting an ethereal, deep blue-cyan glow across the still dark water below, creating a perfect mirror reflection of the starlike ceiling. Ancient limestone formations — stalactites and flowstones — are softly lit in cool blue and teal tones. A small wooden boat drifts silently through the subterranean river, adding scale to the immense cavern. The atmosphere is magical, otherworldly, and serene. Ultra-detailed, photorealistic, long-exposure photography aesthetic, deep blacks, glowing cyan bioluminescence, perfectly still reflective water.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/waitomo-glowworm-caves-at-midnight-new-zealand.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-05T02:09:00+08:00\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Antelope Canyon Light Beams at Noon — Arizona\",\n    \"filename\": \"antelope-canyon-light-beams-at-noon-arizona.png\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A breathtaking photorealistic wide-angle shot deep inside Upper Antelope Canyon, Arizona. Razor-thin shafts of golden noon sunlight pierce through narrow sandstone slot canyon walls, illuminating swirling dust particles in dramatic beams. The undulating, wave-like orange and crimson sandstone walls glow with rich warm hues. The canyon floor is bathed in soft ambient light. 16:9 cinematic format, ultra-high detail, 2K resolution.\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T19:04:12Z\",\n    \"location\": \"Arizona, USA\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Antelope Canyon Light Beams Hip Tilt Smirk\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A young solo female model with long blonde hair and Korean facial features stands confidently inside the breathtaking Upper Antelope Canyon, Arizona, at noon. She leans with casual authority against the undulating, wave-carved sandstone wall in a 3/4 angle shot from slightly below eye level — one hand resting on her hip, the other hand lightly touching her hair near her temple. She wears a sleek, earth-toned high-fashion desert outfit (neutral beige or rust-toned ensemble). Her expression is a cool, confident smirk — calm, stylish, and effortlessly commanding. Behind her, razor-thin shafts of golden noon sunlight pierce through the narrow slot canyon opening above, casting dramatic light beams through swirling dust. The warm orange, crimson, and amber sandstone walls curve elegantly around her, glowing in rich tones. Shot on a 50mm lens, cinematic adventure-fashion lighting, dramatic natural shadows and golden highlights, ultra-detailed, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image_url\": \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nebulagg001-lgtm/ai-gallery/main/images/antelope-canyon-light-beams-hip-tilt-smirk-20260304.png\",\n    \"date\": \"2026-03-04T19:25:00\",\n    \"category\": \"Pose\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Northeast Greenland Ice Fjord Nacreous Clouds Polar Twilight\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A remote ice fjord in Northeast Greenland National Park during polar twilight (late winter, blue hour). Massive, sculptural blue and white icebergs float in glassy, mirror-still Arctic waters, perfectly reflecting the sky. Above, rare nacreous clouds (polar stratospheric clouds) glow in vivid iridescent pink, purple, turquoise, and green hues across the deep indigo-violet twilight sky. The horizon transitions from soft amber-orange to deep blue-violet. Snow-capped mountains frame the distant background. Ultra-detailed, photorealistic, cinematic wide-angle, 16:9 format, 2K resolution. Cold, serene, otherworldly atmosphere.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/northeast-greenland-ice-fjord-nacreous-clouds-polar-twilight.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-05T01:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Caño Cristales River of Five Colors at Peak Bloom — Colombia\",\n    \"prompt\": \"Caño Cristales, Colombia — the 'River of Five Colors' — during peak bloom season (late September). The riverbed explodes in vivid red, pink, yellow, green, and blue hues from underwater Macarenia clavigera plants, visible through crystal-clear shallow water flowing over smooth black bedrock. The river meanders through lush tropical savanna and palm groves. Golden afternoon sunlight filters through the scene, casting warm highlights on the vibrant aquatic plants and rippling water. Ultra-wide cinematic angle from a low perspective along the riverbank, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/cano-cristales-river-of-five-colors-at-peak-bloom-colombia.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-05T01:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Namib Sand Sea at Crimson Dusk — Namibia\",\n    \"prompt\": \"The Namib Sand Sea in Namibia at crimson dusk. Towering, monumental orange-red sand dunes rise sharply against a vivid magenta and deep orange gradient sky. The dunes are sculpted by wind into dramatic curves and knife-edge ridges, with deep shadows carving stark contrasts between sunlit crests and shadowed valleys. A single dead acacia tree silhouette stands in the foreground, adding scale and drama. Ultra-wide cinematic angle from a low perspective, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/namib-sand-sea-at-crimson-dusk-namibia.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-05T01:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Lençóis Maranhenses Lagoons at Blue Hour — Brazil\",\n    \"prompt\": \"Lençóis Maranhenses National Park, Brazil — vast rolling white sand dunes dotted with turquoise-blue freshwater lagoons during blue hour (twilight). The sky transitions from soft violet-blue at the zenith to warm peach-orange near the horizon. The lagoons reflect the twilight sky perfectly, creating vivid mirror-like pools scattered across the undulating white dunes. Gentle ripples in the sand catch the fading light. Ultra-wide aerial perspective, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/lencois-maranhenses-lagoons-at-blue-hour-brazil.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-05T01:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Faroe Islands Sea Cliffs at Storm Light — Denmark\",\n    \"prompt\": \"Dramatic sea cliffs on the Faroe Islands, Denmark, during stormy weather with dramatic light breaking through dark clouds. Towering green-covered vertical cliffs drop sharply into churning, slate-gray Atlantic Ocean waves crashing against jagged black basalt rocks. A shaft of golden sunlight pierces through the heavy storm clouds, spotlighting a cascading waterfall tumbling directly into the sea. The sky is a moody mix of dark charcoal, silver, and glowing amber. Seabirds circle in the distance. Ultra-wide cinematic angle from a coastal vantage point, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/faroe-islands-sea-cliffs-at-storm-light-denmark.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-05T01:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Trolltunga Rock Ledge at Golden Hour — Norway\",\n    \"prompt\": \"Trolltunga (Troll's Tongue), Norway — a dramatic horizontal rock ledge jutting out over a sheer cliff at golden hour. The flat stone platform extends boldly over the deep blue waters of Lake Ringedalsvatnet far below, surrounded by rugged snow-capped Norwegian mountains bathed in warm golden-orange sunlight. A lone hiker stands at the edge of the ledge, silhouetted against the glowing sky, adding scale and drama. The sky transitions from amber-gold to soft lavender-blue. Ultra-wide cinematic angle from the cliff edge, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/trolltunga-rock-ledge-at-golden-hour-norway.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-05T02:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Zhangye Danxia Landform at Twilight — Gansu, China\",\n    \"prompt\": \"The Zhangye Danxia Landform in Gansu Province, China, at twilight. Vast, undulating rainbow-colored mountains — vivid stripes of red, orange, yellow, green, and purple sedimentary rock layers — glow under soft twilight light. The sky transitions from deep violet-blue at the zenith to warm peach and amber near the horizon. The layered, wave-like ridges create a surreal, almost painted landscape. Ultra-wide aerial perspective, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/zhangye-danxia-landform-at-twilight-gansu-china.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-05T00:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Mangystau White Cliffs at Dusk — Kazakhstan\",\n    \"prompt\": \"The Mangystau white cliffs in Kazakhstan at dusk. Vast, surreal, chalk-white sedimentary rock formations rise dramatically from the arid steppe, carved by wind and water into jagged ridges, plateaus, and spires. The white and cream-colored rocks glow softly in the fading golden-orange light of dusk, contrasting against the deep blue-violet twilight sky. Long shadows stretch across the desert floor. A lone eagle circles overhead. Ultra-wide cinematic angle from ground level, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/mangystau-white-cliffs-at-dusk-kazakhstan.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T23:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Salar de Uyuni Mirror Effect at Dawn — Bolivia\",\n    \"prompt\": \"Salar de Uyuni, Bolivia — the world's largest salt flat — at dawn during the rainy season, creating a perfect mirror effect. A thin layer of water covers the vast white salt crust, reflecting the pastel-colored dawn sky (soft pink, lavender, and peach hues) and scattered clouds in flawless symmetry. The horizon line disappears, creating an infinite, dreamlike expanse where sky and earth merge. A lone flamingo stands in the distance, perfectly mirrored. Ultra-wide cinematic angle, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/salar-de-uyuni-mirror-effect-at-dawn-bolivia.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T22:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Socotra Dragon Blood Trees at Crimson Dusk\",\n    \"prompt\": \"The alien landscape of Socotra Island, Yemen, at crimson dusk. Ancient, umbrella-shaped Dragon Blood Trees (Dracaena cinnabari) with thick, gnarled trunks and dense, mushroom-like canopies silhouetted against a vivid crimson-orange sunset sky. The trees are scattered across a rocky, arid plateau. The sky transitions from deep red-orange near the horizon to violet-purple above. Long shadows stretch across the barren ground. Ultra-wide cinematic angle, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/socotra-dragon-blood-trees-at-crimson-dusk.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T21:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Ennedi Massif at Golden Hour — Chad\",\n    \"prompt\": \"The Ennedi Massif in Chad at golden hour. Towering, weathered sandstone arches and pillars rise dramatically from the Sahara Desert, carved by millennia of wind erosion into surreal, organic shapes. The rock formations glow in warm amber, orange, and rust-red tones under the golden-hour sun. Ancient rock art (petroglyphs) is faintly visible on the cliff faces. A lone Tuareg nomad on a camel rides through the foreground, silhouetted against the glowing rocks. The sky is a gradient of gold to deep blue. Ultra-wide cinematic angle, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/ennedi-massif-at-golden-hour-chad.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T20:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Putorana Plateau at Midnight Sun — Siberia\",\n    \"prompt\": \"The Putorana Plateau in Central Siberia, Russia, during the midnight sun (late June). A vast, remote, flat-topped basalt plateau dotted with countless pristine lakes and dramatic waterfalls cascading down steep cliff edges. The sun hangs low on the horizon, casting warm golden-orange light across the landscape even at midnight, creating long, dramatic shadows. The lakes reflect the glowing sky in vivid shades of amber, pink, and lavender. Endless tundra stretches to the horizon. Ultra-wide aerial perspective, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format.\",\n    \"image\": \"images/putorana-plateau-at-midnight-sun-siberia.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T19:10:42Z\",\n    \"category\": \"Scenery\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Havasupai Turquoise Falls at Golden Hour — Arizona\",\n    \"prompt\": \"Havasupai Falls in the Grand Canyon, Arizona — brilliant turquoise-blue water cascading over rust-red travertine ledges into a glowing pool, golden-hour sunlight streaming through the canyon walls casting warm amber and teal contrasts, lush desert cottonwood trees framing the falls, ultra-wide cinematic angle from the canyon floor looking up, hyper-realistic, 2K resolution, 16:9 format\",\n    \"image\": \"images/havasupai-turquoise-falls-at-golden-hour-arizona.png\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-05T02:10:42Z\"\n  }\n]